      "title": "28 IUSF members released on bail",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The 28 members of the Inter-University Students Federation, who were arrested during a protest held on Tuesday (30), were released on bail on Wednesday (31).",
        "They were released on bail after being presented to the Maligakanda Magistrate Court.",
        "The 28 IUSF members were arrested during the protest held by the Inter-University Students' Federation in Maradana area on 10th August.",
        "One-month-old infant abandoned at a motor garage with a letter",
        "Are you a victim of Cyber Crime? Police Unit ready to crackdown crime in the cyberspace"
